    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Deep within you is your spirit,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Even deeper than your “heart”;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Many other things can fill you—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Only Jesus can fill this part."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You have been so empty all these years;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In spite of all you’ve tried, you’re still not satisfied."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Don’t you feel a longing deep within"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To open up and take Christ in?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Doesn’t matter how you see things,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For in God’s eyes “all have sinned”;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus shed His blood to cleanse you"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For the purpose of getting in."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s done everything there is to do,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And He’s the Spirit now so He can get in you."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Makes no difference what your past has been;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The living Christ will still come in."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just as you are in your body,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Perfectly contained therein,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God wants you for His container,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All you need to do is let Him in."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Would you open up from deep within"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To let the Lord come in and fill you to the brim."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Why not open up from deep within"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And call upon the name of Him."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
